<l>viḷintāriṉ vēṟallar maṉṟa teḷintāriṟ</l>
<l>ṟīmai purintoḻuku vār</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Certainly they are no better than dead men who desire evil towards the wife of those who undoubtingly confide in them.</l>
